{"tid":2119703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10月1日軒尼詩道襲警案 督察林泰金證供存在根本性矛盾 裁定被告罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-07-22T08:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T09:27:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"119aa2b2d3bf188354a653df32591ea6729a3536","tid":2119703,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7213&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=e7cdef4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7213</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#崔美霞裁判官 #裁決 <br />\n👤魏(29) #1001灣仔<br />\n<br />\n控罪：#襲擊警務人員 <br />\n<br />\n裁決：罪名不成立🎉<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n判詞後補<br />\n<br />\n因控方證人一林泰金及控方證人二的證供存在根本性矛盾，且無法確立現場環境或受襲經過&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"4ad9babbb615aad4af666743786daff021537b49","tid":2119703,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3737a2b6b1de958617490e7bfc1eaee228b0805","tid":2119703,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad9babbb615aad4af666743786daff021537b49","tid":2119703,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces